title: Need Help Climbing as Tryndamere? (OCE)
body:
Hi everyone, I'm JaySea

I have full gameplay videos in Challenger - Diamond Elo as Tryndamere with very informative commentary completely focused on specific match ups with occasional smurf games.

The channel gets updated almost daily. I answer all comments and try to impart everything I learned to you guys, almost like free personal coaching for those that are in need. I hope you guys will find this resource very useful. Link is below!

Youtube.com/JaySea

Cheers guys!
